trans-unit.source: Represents a base class for classes that automatically generate fields for data-bound controls that use ASP.NET Dynamic Data features.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en basisklasse for klasser som automatisk genererer felt for databundet kontroller som bruker ASP.NET dynamiske funksjoner.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoFieldsGenerator"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoFieldsGenerator"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Returns a list of the properties of an <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en liste over egenskaper for en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: The list of properties.
trans-unit.target: Listen over egenskaper.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that indicates whether enumeration fields should be generated by this <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoFieldsGenerator"></xref> instance.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om opplisting felt skal genereres av dette <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoFieldsGenerator"> </xref> forekomsten.

trans-unit.source: If this flag is not set, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoFieldsGenerator> instance uses the <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.RenderingCompatibility%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Control> class to determine the default behavior.
trans-unit.target: Hvis dette flagget ikke er angitt, den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoFieldsGenerator>serverforekomsten bruker den <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.RenderingCompatibility%2A>for den <xref:System.Web.UI.Control>klassen for å fastslå standard virkemåte.</xref:System.Web.UI.Control> </xref:System.Web.UI.Control.RenderingCompatibility%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoFieldsGenerator>

trans-unit.source: In that case, AutoGenerateEnumFields is set to `true` when <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.RenderingCompatibility%2A> represents version 4.5 or later, and `false` in older versions.
trans-unit.target: I dette tilfellet AutoGenerateEnumFields er satt til `true` når <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.RenderingCompatibility%2A>representerer versjon 4.5 eller senere, og `false` i eldre versjoner.</xref:System.Web.UI.Control.RenderingCompatibility%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if fields should be generated; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis felt skal genereres; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Creates one or more autogenerated fields using the specified collection of field properties.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter ett eller flere felt i generert automatisk ved hjelp av den angitte samlingen for egenskaper.

trans-unit.source: This method sets the header text and sort expression of the field to the `Name` value of `fieldProperties`, sets the `ReadOnly` property of the field to the `IsReadOnly` value of `fieldProperties`, and sets the `DataType` property of the field to the Type value of `fieldProperties`.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden angir hodet tekst og sortering uttrykk for feltet for å den `Name` verdien for `fieldProperties`, angir den `ReadOnly` for felt til den `IsReadOnly` verdien for `fieldProperties`, og angir den `DataType` for feltet av typen verdien `fieldProperties`.

trans-unit.source: This method can be overridden to create a different field.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden kan overstyres for å opprette et annet felt.

trans-unit.source: The list of properties to use when creating the field.
trans-unit.target: Listen over egenskapene som skal brukes når du oppretter feltet.

trans-unit.source: The autogenerated field.
trans-unit.target: Feltet automatisk generert.

trans-unit.source: When implemented in a derived class, creates autogenerated fields based on the current data item.
trans-unit.target: Når implementert i en avledet klasse, opprettes det automatisk genererte felt basert på gjeldende dataelement.

trans-unit.source: This method typically populates the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoFieldsGenerator.AutoGeneratedFieldProperties%2A> collection.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden vanligvis fyller ut den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoFieldsGenerator.AutoGeneratedFieldProperties%2A>samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoFieldsGenerator.AutoGeneratedFieldProperties%2A>

trans-unit.source: The current data item.
trans-unit.target: Gjeldende dataelement.

trans-unit.source: The data-bound control that will contain the autogenerated fields.
trans-unit.target: Databundet kontrollen som inneholder automatisk genererte-felt.

trans-unit.source: The autogenerated fields.
trans-unit.target: Automatisk genererte-felt.

trans-unit.source: Creates <xref href="System.Web.DynamicData.DynamicField"></xref> objects based on metadata information for the table.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter <xref href="System.Web.DynamicData.DynamicField"> </xref> objekter som er basert på metadatainformasjon for tabellen.
